{
  "stem": "210.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And people are constantly got killed when they went out of the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was just like raining bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And but it was lucky that there was food-- you know, cans and things in the thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were-- this camp were, like, some Poles, mostly men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Not mostly-- all men.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Poles, Russians, French were in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they took out all the sick people from the-- from the hospitals.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there were no Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There were other-- because there were no Jews in that camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they took them all down into the-- into the-- into the bunkers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, we saw the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Russians came and they liberated us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was also chaos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We had to hide from them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were-- they were raping the girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was terrible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we just wanted to get out of there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were no-- it was no transportation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was no nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was only these trains going with the people from-- the wounded that they were taking back from the front and the Russian and German prisoners of war and mostly Russians.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we, we stayed there for about a week after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And you know, we-- some, they were sick.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "A lot of them were sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And they were taken to hospitals.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And the other ones were just left to fend for themselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we found one Russian, you know, higher up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he, you know, brought us clothes and food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And the clothes were, like, I came home to Lodz in a men's coat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Whatever they gave you-- whatever they had, they gave you.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
